<em><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Thoth&#32;reigned&#32;supreme.&#32;His&#32;freshly&#32;formed&#32;vassals&#32;flooded&#32;into&#32;their&#32;new&#32;home&#32;by&#32;the&#32;millions.&#32;They&#32;would&#32;make&#32;excellent&#32;workhorses&#32;for&#32;the&#32;nobles....</span></em></div>
    
    
    
